---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Free Financial Tools & Calculators"
  description="Free financial calculators from Jason Ehlinger — investment calculator, retirement calculator, compound interest calculator, and more. Build your wealth with the right numbers."
  keywords="free financial calculators, investment calculator, retirement calculator, compound interest calculator, wealth building tools, personal finance tools"
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="section-label">Free Resources</span>
    <h1>Financial Tools & Calculators</h1>
    <p>Numbers don't lie. Use these free tools to see exactly where you stand — and where you're headed.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:960px;">

      <div class="tools-grid">

        <a href="/tools/investment-calculator" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-icon">📈</div>
          <h2>Investment Calculator</h2>
          <p>See how your money grows over time with compound returns. Adjust your initial investment, monthly contribution, rate of return, and time horizon.</p>
          <span class="tool-cta">Use Calculator →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/retirement-calculator" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-icon">🏁</div>
          <h2>Retirement Calculator</h2>
          <p>Find out if you're on track to retire with enough. Enter your current savings, age, and contributions to get your projected retirement number and income.</p>
          <span class="tool-cta">Use Calculator →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/compound-interest-calculator" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-icon">⚡</div>
          <h2>Compound Interest Calculator</h2>
          <p>Watch compound interest work its magic. See a year-by-year breakdown of how interest earns interest — and why starting early changes everything.</p>
          <span class="tool-cta">Use Calculator →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/mortgage-calculator" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-icon">🏠</div>
          <h2>Mortgage Calculator</h2>
          <p>See how much house you can afford the smart way — a 15-year fixed mortgage with a payment no more than 25% of your take-home pay. Includes a full PITI breakdown.</p>
          <span class="tool-cta">Use Calculator →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/zero-based-budget" class="tool-card" style="border-color:var(--gold); grid-column: 1 / -1;">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:1.5rem;">
            <div class="tool-icon" style="font-size:2.5rem; margin:0;">💰</div>
            <div style="flex:1;">
              <h2 style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Zero-Based Budget Builder</h2>
              <p style="margin:0;">Give every dollar a job before the month starts. Fill in your income and all expense categories online — then download a branded PDF of your complete budget plan.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="tool-cta" style="white-space:nowrap;">Build Your Budget →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>

      <!-- CTA STRIP -->
      <div style="margin-top:4rem; background:var(--black); color:var(--white); padding:3rem 2rem; border-radius:4px; text-align:center;">
        <span class="section-label">Go Deeper</span>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Numbers Are a Starting Point. A Plan Is What Changes Things.</h2>
        <p style="color:#ccc; margin-bottom:2rem; max-width:560px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;">I've built a 7-figure company on a budget that started at zero. These tools will show you the math — but if you want to actually get there, let's talk.</p>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Book a Free Assessment</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">See How I Can Help</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- YOUTUBE STRIP -->
      <div style="margin-top:3rem; padding:2rem; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px;">
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto; gap:1.5rem; align-items:center;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Vision Tribe Money — Free on YouTube</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">777+ videos on personal finance, wealth building, budgeting, and money in marriage. I go live every Tuesday and Wednesday. Come learn for free.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-dark" style="white-space:nowrap;">Watch Free ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .tool-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .tool-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .tool-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .tool-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .tool-card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .tool-cta {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tools-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
